item.title: I have some questions for uploading a client
item.dc:creator: @mista_pnut mista pnut
item.description:
@mista_pnut wrote:

You don’t really need to delete any. I suggest doing the following though if you’re going to give a downloadable client that isn’t a .jar.

Delete all java files(Make sure to compile before)
Delete Compiler
Hide all class files
Hide all folders
Only files showing should be the ones to run the client
